"title": "5939: satisfaction",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5939: satisfaction",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A state of contentment or fulfilment. Only God brings true satisfaction and Scripture advocates that believers should cultivate satisfaction in every situation. Jesus Christ's atoning death was the unique means of satisfying the demands of the law.</p>\n<h2>Satisfaction of hunger and thirst</h2>\n<h3>Literal</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:30\">PRO 6:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:26\">LEV 26:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut14:29\">DEU 14:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut26:12\">DEU 26:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:39-Job38:41\">JOB 38:39–38:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:26\">PSA 22:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps59:15\">PSA 59:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps105:40\">PSA 105:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps132:15\">PSA 132:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:14\">PSA 147:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl6:7\">ECC 6:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:25\">JER 31:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos13:6\">HOS 13:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:19\">JOL 2:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:14\">MIC 6:14</a></p>\n<h3>Metaphorical</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:13\">PSA 104:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:25-Job38:27\">JOB 38:25–38:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:11\">ISA 66:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer46:10\">JER 46:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:19\">JER 50:19</a></p>\n<h2>Satisfaction in one's work</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl3:13\">ECC 3:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:24\">ECC 2:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:18\">ECC 5:18</a></p>\n<h2>Satisfaction with one's situation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:5\">HEB 13:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:14\">LUK 3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:10-Phil4:13\">PHP 4:10–4:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:6-1Tim6:8\">1TI 6:6–6:8</a></p>\n<h2>Spiritual satisfaction</h2>\n<h3>Found in God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps17:15\">PSA 17:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps63:1-Ps63:5\">PSA 63:1–63:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps81:13-Ps81:16\">PSA 81:13–81:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps90:14\">PSA 90:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:23\">PRO 19:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:1-Isa55:2\">ISA 55:1–55:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:21\">LUK 6:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:7-John4:15\">JHN 4:7–4:15</a></p>\n<h3>As a result of God's good provision</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:16\">PSA 145:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:10\">DEU 8:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut11:15\">DEU 11:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:16\">PSA 91:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:8-Ps107:9\">PSA 107:8–107:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:9-Isa58:11\">ISA 58:9–58:11</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ satisfies the hungry</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:15-Matt14:20\">MAT 14:15–14:20</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:35-Mark6:44\">MRK 6:35–6:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:12-Luke9:17\">LUK 9:12–9:17</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:32-Matt15:37\">MAT 15:32–15:37</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:2-Mark8:8\">MRK 8:2–8:8</a></p>\n<h2>Dissatisfaction</h2>\n<h3>Riches do not bring satisfaction</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:10\">ECC 5:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth5:10-Esth5:13\">EST 5:10–5:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl4:8\">ECC 4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek7:19\">EZK 7:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:13-Luke12:21\">LUK 12:13–12:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:7-1Tim6:10\">1TI 6:7–6:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:5\">HEB 13:5</a></p>\n<h3>Death is never satisfied</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:20\">PRO 27:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov30:15-Prov30:16\">PRO 30:15–30:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:5\">HAB 2:5</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's satisfaction of the demands of the law</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:21\">2CO 5:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:26-Heb7:28\">HEB 7:26–7:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:11-Heb9:14\">HEB 9:11–9:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:25-Heb10:10\">HEB 9:25–10:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:12-Heb10:14\">HEB 10:12–10:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:18\">1PE 3:18</a></p>",
